parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the camshaft position sensor can cause the engine to stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded. It can also cause an underhood fire, which can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The check engine light illuminates
the engine stalls
the vehicle makes an odd noise
the vehicle intermittently stalls at various speeds
grey smoke erupts from under the hood
and the vehicle has a burning smell.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The difficulty in shifting gears can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS system can cause the vehicle to lose braking ability, leading to increased stopping distances and potential accidents.
symptoms: The ABS light comes on and off when hitting the brakes
the brake pads are coming off the rotors
making a weird noise
the brake pedal comes up a little bit.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake pedal can cause the vehicle to lose braking ability, leading to increased stopping distances and potential accidents.
symptoms: The brake pedal goes to the floor
the vehicle does not stop when the brakes are applied
the brake pedal feels soft or spongy.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the timing belt and tensioner can cause the vehicle to stop suddenly, leading to potential accidents, and can also cause damage to the engine, including the heads and valves.
symptoms: The tensioner pulley breaks
the timing belt is thrown
the vehicle stops suddenly
the engine is damaged
including the heads and valves.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake rotors and pads can cause the vehicle to lose braking ability, leading to increased stopping distances and potential accidents.
symptoms: The brake pads and rotors need to be replaced frequently
the brake pads are coming off the rotors
making a weird noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The degradation of the dashboard material can cause it to crack, break, or come apart, which can lead to a distraction for the driver, obstruct the driver's view, and potentially cause an accident.
symptoms: The dashboard is cracking
breaking
or coming apart near the windshield and front of the steering wheel.
